rows.label: qst003401_msg0001
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Hey, come on. Give me a break!

rows.label: qst003401_msg0002
rows.name:
We're selling our stuff as cheap as can
be!

rows.label: qst003401_msg0003
rows.name:
This Superbian factory stuff's right over
the odds!

rows.label: qst003401_msg0004
rows.name:
And now the water supply's off! When
are they going to fix that ruddy water
tower?

rows.label: qst003401_msg0005
rows.name:
How am I supposed to raise my leeks
without water? I wish these smart-arse
Superbians had an answer to that!

rows.label: qst003401_msg0101
rows.name:
Give over will ya? It wasn't us
Superbians who smashed up the
water tower.

rows.label: qst003401_msg0102
rows.name: The people who did that are...

rows.label: qst003401_msg0103
rows.name:
...those Drivers over there! If you want
to complain, complain to those wee
bastards!

rows.label: qst003401_msg0104
rows.name:
What? That's who smashed up our
lovely water tower?

rows.label: qst003401_msg0105
rows.name:
Thanks to your little demolition job,
I've got to lug water by hand to my
fields. It's doing my back in!

rows.label: qst003401_msg0106
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]I think I'll take my mind off it by giving
your arses a little kick!

rows.label: qst003401_msg0202
rows.name:
I apologize for inconveniencing you
like this, ma'am.

rows.label: qst003401_msg0203
rows.name:
'Inconveniencing'? That's a fine way
of putting it. We're just trying to have
a civil talk about important stuff!

rows.label: qst003401_msg0204
rows.name:
Hey, you. Are you this soldier's
superior or something?

rows.label: qst003401_msg0205
rows.name:
Then I guess you won't listen to us
any better than he does.

rows.label: qst003401_msg0206
rows.name:
Nae bother.
Let us make it crystal clear!
